dct_title_s: Turquie d'Asie : Caucase - Perse - Égypte / édité par les Cartes Taride.
dct_description_sm: Map shows French and British Mandate Territories, international and vilayets boundaries, railways in use and in construction, roads, rivers, canals, and ruins. Includes 2 inset map: [northern Africa for map continued to west, at scale 1:8.800,000] -- [Asia; scale 1:35.000,000]. Map shows Greenwich and Paris prime meridians.
